1
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,918
=Vanished Name=

2
00:01:35,224 --> 00:01:37,816
=Episode 19=
(University)

3
00:01:40,812 --> 00:01:42,213
(Winter break is over.)

4
00:01:42,732 --> 00:01:44,612
(Before making up with Mom and Xiaofei,)

5
00:01:45,573 --> 00:01:47,224
(I rushed back to school.)

6
00:01:48,013 --> 00:01:51,573
(A short winter break
left me alienated from everyone.)

7
00:02:07,576 --> 00:02:09,784
(Exam Room No. 112)

8
00:02:17,144 --> 00:02:18,892
(For the three days of the gaokao exam,)

9
00:02:18,892 --> 00:02:20,728
(Bai Shu and I were
in different exam rooms,)

10
00:02:21,013 --> 00:02:22,612
(so I never saw her.)

11
00:02:26,212 --> 00:02:28,052
(The final bell for the exam rang.)

12
00:02:28,373 --> 00:02:31,452
(One chapter of life ended,
and another was about to begin.)

13
00:02:34,813 --> 00:02:37,772
(At that moment,
all the classmates around me vanished,)

14
00:02:38,452 --> 00:02:40,853
(and loneliness surged from all sides.)

15
00:02:42,212 --> 00:02:44,853
(For many people,
fate began to differ right here.)

16
00:02:46,253 --> 00:02:49,172
(But I just didn't realize it
at the time.)

17
00:03:05,093 --> 00:03:06,413
I knew you'd be here.

18
00:03:06,552 --> 00:03:08,732
What? Didn't do well?

19
00:03:11,133 --> 00:03:12,452
Why are you here?

20
00:03:13,133 --> 00:03:14,693
Why didn't you tell me?

21
00:03:15,813 --> 00:03:17,293
I came back the day before the exam.

22
00:03:18,693 --> 00:03:20,772
I wanted to find you
during those three exam days,

23
00:03:21,892 --> 00:03:23,288
but I didn't know your exam room.

24
00:03:24,052 --> 00:03:25,452
I thought you weren't taking it.

25
00:03:25,732 --> 00:03:27,052
You scared me.

26
00:03:34,813 --> 00:03:37,172
How did your face get so tan?

27
00:03:40,408 --> 00:03:43,573
Out at the beach all day under the sun,
of course I get tan.

28
00:03:46,293 --> 00:03:47,253
Was the beach fun?

29
00:03:51,693 --> 00:03:52,732
I learned to scuba dive.

30
00:03:54,013 --> 00:03:56,732
The seabed was incredibly beautiful,
with colorful coral

31
00:03:57,772 --> 00:03:59,212
and all kinds of tropical fish.

32
00:04:00,373 --> 00:04:03,452
The best part was the absolute silence
underwater.

33
00:04:04,533 --> 00:04:05,332
It was so quiet.

34
00:04:08,772 --> 00:04:11,093
I thought you were in deep trouble,

35
00:04:12,172 --> 00:04:14,093
but turns out you were living it up.

36
00:04:18,332 --> 00:04:20,693
I was just trying
to avoid being in the same room as her.

37
00:04:22,253 --> 00:04:24,212
Scuba diving was the only thing
she let me do,

38
00:04:25,733 --> 00:04:27,613
probably figured
I couldn't escape in the ocean.

39
00:04:34,573 --> 00:04:36,088
How many points do you think you got?

40
00:04:37,173 --> 00:04:38,212
What about you?

41
00:04:44,984 --> 00:04:47,292
I think it's probably
similar to yours this time.

42
00:04:48,412 --> 00:04:50,532
You haven't been to school
for such a long time.

43
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:53,092
I won't burst your bubble.
You tell me first.

44
00:04:56,332 --> 00:05:00,332
I estimate around 720 points.

45
00:05:00,933 --> 00:05:03,933
Because my approach to one math problem
was beyond the curriculum.

46
00:05:04,332 --> 00:05:04,933
How much?

47
00:05:05,693 --> 00:05:06,892
Around 720.

48
00:05:07,573 --> 00:05:08,184
What?

49
00:05:09,652 --> 00:05:12,733
Oh my! How can you be so unfair?

50
00:05:13,013 --> 00:05:15,053
She had fun every day
and scored that much?

51
00:05:15,373 --> 00:05:17,972
But me? I worked so hard
and scored lower than her?

52
00:05:20,053 --> 00:05:21,292
What score did you estimate?

53
00:05:21,573 --> 00:05:22,813
Don't talk to me.

54
00:05:22,968 --> 00:05:24,133
I'm complaining of my life.

55
00:05:33,892 --> 00:05:35,933
(Ren Xiaoming, total score: 660 points)
660?

56
00:05:38,872 --> 00:05:42,652
Ren Xiaoming, you're amazing!

57
00:05:44,092 --> 00:05:45,212
Get lost!

58
00:05:45,212 --> 00:05:47,972
You scored 60 points higher than me,
and you think I'm amazing?

59
00:05:50,652 --> 00:05:55,253
Great! We can go to Qingzhou together!

60
00:06:03,013 --> 00:06:04,652
She lets you go to college in Qingzhou?

61
00:06:08,133 --> 00:06:11,212
She hasn't interfered
with my choices these days.

62
00:06:11,652 --> 00:06:13,452
Since coming home
after Chinese New Year,

63
00:06:14,053 --> 00:06:16,693
she hasn't mentioned the exam
or college at all.

64
00:06:20,332 --> 00:06:21,613
Maybe she really came around?

65
00:06:24,733 --> 00:06:27,092
Just fill in your choices
however you want.

66
00:06:27,173 --> 00:06:28,733
Don't worry about what she thinks.

67
00:06:37,253 --> 00:06:38,852
I wonder how He Yuqiong did.

68
00:06:44,332 --> 00:06:46,573
Paid the hospital fee?
How much did it cost?

69
00:06:48,452 --> 00:06:50,573
What? Not enough money?

70
00:06:51,452 --> 00:06:53,053
Paid it all. Not a cent left.

71
00:06:53,733 --> 00:06:55,173
How are we supposed to live now?

72
00:06:59,772 --> 00:07:02,092
Mom, you've been up all night.
You should go home and rest.

73
00:07:02,424 --> 00:07:03,133
I'll stay.

74
00:07:03,332 --> 00:07:04,013
Alright.

75
00:07:04,292 --> 00:07:06,292
You keep an eye on him.
I'll come tonight.

76
00:07:06,373 --> 00:07:06,904
Okay.

77
00:07:11,652 --> 00:07:13,972
Actually, your dad lying here

78
00:07:14,133 --> 00:07:15,933
is better than
when he acts like a scoundrel.

79
00:07:16,813 --> 00:07:18,532
If he recovers,
he might still act the same.

80
00:07:19,253 --> 00:07:20,253
Don't say that.

81
00:07:20,613 --> 00:07:24,373
I know you always have
a soft spot for your dad.

82
00:07:24,573 --> 00:07:25,532
You care about him.

83
00:07:26,813 --> 00:07:28,573
I just don't want him to die like this.

84
00:07:30,173 --> 00:07:32,573
I want him to realize
how much of a scoundrel he was.

85
00:07:35,332 --> 00:07:39,104
The person your dad wronged the most
in his life isn't me, but you.

86
00:07:40,184 --> 00:07:41,972
You used to love being with him.

87
00:07:42,573 --> 00:07:43,813
He let you down.

88
00:07:44,693 --> 00:07:46,733
Not only didn't he
bring you anything good,

89
00:07:47,332 --> 00:07:49,133
but also he got into trouble
during your exam.

90
00:07:49,133 --> 00:07:49,656
Mom.

91
00:07:50,652 --> 00:07:51,928
I don't want to go to college.

92
00:07:52,053 --> 00:07:53,212
I want to learn a trade.

93
00:07:53,784 --> 00:07:54,652
No way.

94
00:07:55,292 --> 00:07:56,412
You go to a cram school.

95
00:07:56,852 --> 00:07:57,733
I can't hold you back.

96
00:07:58,133 --> 00:08:00,332
Cram school?
I'm just not cut out for it.

97
00:08:01,173 --> 00:08:01,892
Look,

98
00:08:02,212 --> 00:08:03,733
him lying there costs us money,

99
00:08:04,173 --> 00:08:06,133
and me going to college costs even more.

100
00:08:06,532 --> 00:08:07,772
We can't just spend money.

101
00:08:07,892 --> 00:08:09,412
We need to find ways to make money.

102
00:08:09,733 --> 00:08:11,693
When I make big money,

103
00:08:11,892 --> 00:08:14,652
I'll get you a big house,
a nice car, and a dog.

104
00:08:15,133 --> 00:08:16,216
We three travel the world.

105
00:08:16,613 --> 00:08:17,332
What do you think?

106
00:08:18,053 --> 00:08:20,952
Son, you were just born wrong.

107
00:08:22,212 --> 00:08:25,013
How did you end up being my son?

108
00:08:25,452 --> 00:08:26,292
Miserable!

109
00:08:26,573 --> 00:08:28,292
What do you mean?

110
00:08:28,373 --> 00:08:29,452
It's only making money.

111
00:08:29,852 --> 00:08:32,532
Many kids younger than me
have gone out to work and earn money.

112
00:08:32,892 --> 00:08:33,772
What's the big deal?

113
00:08:34,253 --> 00:08:34,853
It's nothing.

114
00:08:36,373 --> 00:08:37,572
I know everything.

115
00:08:38,373 --> 00:08:40,253
I know what you think.

116
00:08:41,093 --> 00:08:44,408
Xiaoming is going to college.

117
00:08:45,733 --> 00:08:46,613
Don't mention her.

118
00:08:47,613 --> 00:08:48,652
We're not in touch.

119
00:08:50,213 --> 00:08:53,172
She goes her way.
We're on different paths.

120
00:08:54,373 --> 00:08:56,292
Then... you two...

121
00:08:57,973 --> 00:08:59,412
Mom, stop worrying about me.

122
00:08:59,613 --> 00:09:01,253
It's fine. Go home and rest.

123
00:09:01,464 --> 00:09:03,412
Take a nap and come back tonight.

124
00:09:36,333 --> 00:09:37,532
Qingzhou is so far away.

125
00:09:38,453 --> 00:09:40,213
How will I take care of you?

126
00:09:43,652 --> 00:09:44,973
I can take care of myself.

127
00:09:46,453 --> 00:09:49,253
I have been taking care of you
since you were little.

128
00:09:49,613 --> 00:09:51,172
How could you take care of yourself?

129
00:09:51,733 --> 00:09:54,213
Just do as I say,
you go to school in La City.

130
00:09:54,572 --> 00:09:55,892
So many good colleges in La City.

131
00:09:56,013 --> 00:09:58,652
You can study whatever major you want.

132
00:09:59,096 --> 00:09:59,733
Okay?

133
00:10:01,532 --> 00:10:02,973
I want to go to Qingzhou.

134
00:10:06,253 --> 00:10:07,853
Because of Ren Xiaoming?

135
00:10:09,853 --> 00:10:12,932
I heard she applied
to a college in Qingzhou too.

136
00:10:13,772 --> 00:10:15,133
You were led astray by her.

137
00:10:15,932 --> 00:10:17,532
It has nothing to do with Xiaoming.

138
00:10:19,853 --> 00:10:21,493
Are you determined to go to Qingzhou?

139
00:10:23,932 --> 00:10:24,532
Fine.

140
00:10:26,093 --> 00:10:27,692
Then Ren Xiaoming won't be going.

141
00:10:29,692 --> 00:10:30,772
What do you want to do?

142
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,812
Do I need to explain everything to you?

143
00:10:34,013 --> 00:10:36,532
You know I am capable of doing this.

144
00:10:37,333 --> 00:10:39,544
Only one of you two can go.

145
00:10:41,772 --> 00:10:42,532
You choose.

146
00:10:55,052 --> 00:10:57,373
What's wrong, Ms. Zhao? Who upset you?

147
00:10:57,453 --> 00:10:59,532
My star student Bai Shu...

148
00:11:00,973 --> 00:11:03,292
Her mother just changed her choice.

149
00:11:03,733 --> 00:11:04,772
To where?

150
00:11:05,373 --> 00:11:07,532
A local college in La City.

151
00:11:08,504 --> 00:11:09,080
Excuse me.

152
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,960
Her mother seems educated.
How could she be so foolish?

153
00:11:12,333 --> 00:11:13,613
What a waste.

154
00:11:13,613 --> 00:11:16,772
Exactly, this kid has potential
to go to Qingzhou University.

155
00:11:17,453 --> 00:11:18,136
Excuse me.

156
00:11:19,453 --> 00:11:20,213
Come in.

157
00:11:23,213 --> 00:11:25,532
Miss, I'm here to submit
my college preference form.

158
00:11:25,892 --> 00:11:26,973
Why are you so late?

159
00:11:29,453 --> 00:11:30,973
Miss, I just heard you say

160
00:11:31,453 --> 00:11:33,052
Bai Shu changed her choice?

161
00:11:33,412 --> 00:11:34,572
Not Qingzhou University?

162
00:11:36,172 --> 00:11:36,932
We had no choice.

163
00:11:37,172 --> 00:11:39,172
Her mother went all the way
to the principal.

164
00:11:39,453 --> 00:11:43,133
And the principal tried convincing her
so hard, but still failed.

165
00:11:43,532 --> 00:11:47,160
No matter how high our hopes for students,
we must respect the parents' wishes.

166
00:11:48,853 --> 00:11:49,613
Goodbye, Ms. Zhao.

167
00:11:59,333 --> 00:12:00,052
What's going on?

168
00:12:01,292 --> 00:12:02,532
What's going on?

169
00:12:02,932 --> 00:12:04,472
- I was taking pictures.
- What for?

170
00:12:04,932 --> 00:12:06,172
What choice did you fill in?

171
00:12:06,172 --> 00:12:07,093
Which college?

172
00:12:07,932 --> 00:12:08,572
Xiaoming.

173
00:12:09,973 --> 00:12:10,652
Forget it.

174
00:12:12,213 --> 00:12:13,613
I just don't want to go anymore.

175
00:12:14,932 --> 00:12:15,892
Qingzhou is too far.

176
00:12:17,412 --> 00:12:17,973
Don't lie.

177
00:12:18,892 --> 00:12:21,013
You promised. You must change it back.

178
00:12:22,532 --> 00:12:23,864
I'll go for the graduation photo.

179
00:12:29,172 --> 00:12:30,412
Did she threaten you with me?

180
00:12:30,772 --> 00:12:32,093
Did she use me to threaten you?

181
00:12:32,292 --> 00:12:33,013
No.

182
00:12:34,692 --> 00:12:35,532
Liar.

183
00:12:35,973 --> 00:12:36,692
Come on.

184
00:12:38,172 --> 00:12:39,013
I won't change it.

185
00:12:39,652 --> 00:12:41,213
She won't let you go to Qingzhou.

186
00:12:41,652 --> 00:12:42,892
She means what she says.

187
00:12:43,692 --> 00:12:44,812
Remember the bun incident?

188
00:12:47,384 --> 00:12:48,333
I knew it.

189
00:12:48,696 --> 00:12:50,453
You go to university in Qingzhou.

190
00:12:52,733 --> 00:12:53,812
Don't worry about me.

191
00:12:54,733 --> 00:12:56,572
If the sky falls,
the tall ones hold it up.

192
00:12:57,013 --> 00:12:59,093
I'm taller than you,
so I should hold it up.

193
00:13:01,652 --> 00:13:04,733
Even if I have to drop out,
I'll fight her to the end.

194
00:13:06,412 --> 00:13:07,572
Ten years of hard study.

195
00:13:08,632 --> 00:13:09,692
You worked so hard.

196
00:13:11,853 --> 00:13:12,532
You can't...

197
00:13:12,532 --> 00:13:15,853
If it weren't for you,
I couldn't have gotten into Yucai.

198
00:13:16,613 --> 00:13:19,692
If it weren't for you, I wouldn't dream of
getting into a college in Qingzhou.

199
00:13:22,133 --> 00:13:24,613
Getting into Yucai with you,

200
00:13:25,932 --> 00:13:27,093
I'm perfectly content.

201
00:13:28,892 --> 00:13:30,532
Wherever I go next doesn't matter.

202
00:13:31,213 --> 00:13:32,733
But whether I can go with you matters.

203
00:13:37,532 --> 00:13:38,213
Xiaoming.

204
00:13:40,412 --> 00:13:40,932
Fine.

205
00:13:42,292 --> 00:13:44,172
You won't change it? Then I will.

206
00:13:44,952 --> 00:13:45,932
I'll go to La City too.

207
00:13:46,812 --> 00:13:49,013
I'll change it. I'll change it, okay?

208
00:13:50,453 --> 00:13:51,412
Don't you change it.

209
00:13:53,733 --> 00:13:54,892
Come on, I'll go with you.

210
00:13:57,093 --> 00:13:59,292
Let's put Qingzhou University
as our first choice.

211
00:13:59,652 --> 00:14:01,133
A La City college as the second one.

212
00:14:01,572 --> 00:14:02,744
Let's go to college together.

213
00:14:03,412 --> 00:14:04,772
Okay, together.

214
00:14:12,093 --> 00:14:12,812
What's up?

215
00:14:12,892 --> 00:14:14,168
To change the preference form.

216
00:14:14,253 --> 00:14:14,853
Who's changing?

217
00:14:15,172 --> 00:14:15,812
I am.

218
00:14:16,292 --> 00:14:17,133
To where?

219
00:14:17,613 --> 00:14:19,013
- First choice: Qingzhou University.
- First choice: Qingzhou University.

220
00:14:20,024 --> 00:14:22,532
Great! Sit here and fill it out.

221
00:14:23,412 --> 00:14:24,373
Be serious.

222
00:14:24,824 --> 00:14:26,456
Luckily, this is the preference form.

223
00:14:26,456 --> 00:14:28,812
If it were the official one,
you wouldn't change it.

224
00:14:30,733 --> 00:14:33,172
My class has finished,
and I'm not in our graduation photo.

225
00:14:33,172 --> 00:14:34,613
No worries, take it with my class.

226
00:14:34,812 --> 00:14:37,093
Give them a chance
to take a photo with the top scorer.

227
00:14:37,213 --> 00:14:38,532
Excuse me, coming through.

228
00:14:38,532 --> 00:14:39,532
Get up here! Hurry up!

229
00:14:39,532 --> 00:14:40,213
- Come over here!
- Come on.

230
00:14:40,213 --> 00:14:41,733
Look this way! Come on.

231
00:14:42,532 --> 00:14:44,013
Three, two, one!

232
00:14:54,532 --> 00:14:58,172
- Three, two, one!
- Three, two, one!

233
00:15:05,013 --> 00:15:07,772
Qingzhou University,
School of International Relations.

234
00:15:08,532 --> 00:15:11,853
I'm one step closer to my dream
of traveling the world.

235
00:15:11,973 --> 00:15:14,613
I'm one step closer to my dream
of making big money.

236
00:15:25,013 --> 00:15:26,093
Can you keep this for me?

237
00:15:29,613 --> 00:15:30,213
Got it.

238
00:15:30,733 --> 00:15:33,052
I'll buy the train tickets too
and keep them with me.

239
00:15:34,093 --> 00:15:36,013
Then you can go
to the station empty-handed.

240
00:15:36,733 --> 00:15:38,213
In Qingzhou, let's do part-time jobs.

241
00:15:38,532 --> 00:15:39,892
We can buy whatever we need.

242
00:15:40,932 --> 00:15:42,692
But I don't think
she'll let me go easily.

243
00:15:46,172 --> 00:15:47,532
I have a bad feeling.

244
00:15:49,253 --> 00:15:52,133
What bad feeling? It's all good.

245
00:15:53,333 --> 00:15:55,613
Once you're in Qingzhou,
how can she control you?

246
00:15:56,373 --> 00:15:58,652
Anyway, we'll face everything together.

247
00:16:01,453 --> 00:16:02,292
Ren Xiaoming.

248
00:16:05,172 --> 00:16:06,213
It's good to have you.

249
00:16:12,733 --> 00:16:15,613
Don't worry. I'm here for you.

250
00:16:27,213 --> 00:16:28,696
We're going to Qingzhou!

251
00:16:28,696 --> 00:16:30,093
We're going to Qingzhou!

252
00:16:30,253 --> 00:16:31,532
We're going to Qingzhou!

253
00:16:31,532 --> 00:16:32,812
All aboard!

254
00:16:50,264 --> 00:16:55,032
(Qidaohezi, 2007)

255
00:17:08,253 --> 00:17:09,213
No need to avoid me.

256
00:17:11,933 --> 00:17:12,852
I'll leave Wednesday.

257
00:17:14,493 --> 00:17:15,812
The train leaves at 7 A.M.

258
00:17:25,092 --> 00:17:27,372
I'll work in Qingzhou during holidays.

259
00:17:29,372 --> 00:17:30,653
We probably won't meet again.

260
00:17:42,173 --> 00:17:42,933
I'm sorry.

261
00:17:45,292 --> 00:17:47,772
I apologize on behalf of my mom,
to you and your mom.

262
00:18:24,132 --> 00:18:26,052
Mom, I'll be out tonight.
You handle this.

263
00:18:33,292 --> 00:18:35,253
This was made in our factory
back in the day.

264
00:18:35,893 --> 00:18:38,812
Couldn't even buy it domestically.
It was for export.

265
00:18:40,824 --> 00:18:42,052
Look at this zipper.

266
00:18:48,612 --> 00:18:50,532
Okay. You keep this treasure, alright?

267
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:51,292
Not for me.

268
00:18:51,352 --> 00:18:54,584
Xiaoming, Mom's suitcase
is much better than your bag.

269
00:18:54,973 --> 00:18:55,852
She has no good taste.

270
00:19:02,092 --> 00:19:03,288
College girl.

271
00:19:06,453 --> 00:19:07,852
I topped up your phone credit.

272
00:19:08,132 --> 00:19:09,213
Tell me when you arrive.

273
00:19:10,173 --> 00:19:11,332
Call home sometimes.

274
00:19:15,013 --> 00:19:16,052
You cheapskate.

275
00:19:16,532 --> 00:19:18,332
You get a new one
and give me the used one?

276
00:19:18,653 --> 00:19:19,612
Then give it back.

277
00:19:19,612 --> 00:19:20,733
I want it.

278
00:19:21,812 --> 00:19:23,532
The news said

279
00:19:23,812 --> 00:19:25,733
poverty alleviation needs
to happen in stages.

280
00:19:25,933 --> 00:19:28,253
Getting rich takes time too.

281
00:19:30,168 --> 00:19:32,092
Xiaoming, use that phone for now.

282
00:19:32,693 --> 00:19:35,372
When I grow up,
I'll buy you a better phone.

283
00:19:36,092 --> 00:19:38,372
Who needs you to buy it?
Trying to show off?

284
00:19:40,332 --> 00:19:41,772
From now on, you'll be on your own.

285
00:19:42,292 --> 00:19:43,973
Be careful of everything.

286
00:19:44,372 --> 00:19:47,173
Alright, I don't need you
to tell me that.

287
00:19:49,132 --> 00:19:51,772
After I die, no one will nag you then.

288
00:19:52,052 --> 00:19:52,933
Pack your own things.

289
00:19:57,132 --> 00:19:58,973
Here, keep this.

290
00:20:00,933 --> 00:20:03,772
Xiaoming, why is Bai Shu's
admission letter with you?

291
00:20:04,092 --> 00:20:06,653
We agreed to go together,
so she left it with me.

292
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:08,453
In my opinion,

293
00:20:09,132 --> 00:20:11,733
Bai Shu will be a big diplomat

294
00:20:12,532 --> 00:20:13,453
and travel the world.

295
00:20:13,852 --> 00:20:16,733
While you'll be stuck indoors
with your major.

296
00:20:17,532 --> 00:20:18,372
No vision.

297
00:20:20,933 --> 00:20:22,092
Why hit me before leaving?

298
00:20:22,653 --> 00:20:25,772
It's because I'm leaving
that I'm hitting you.

299
00:20:26,013 --> 00:20:27,612
So you don't go wild after I'm gone.

300
00:20:28,013 --> 00:20:30,653
How dare you! Only you are the wild one.

301
00:20:30,893 --> 00:20:32,292
We'll have peace once you leave.

302
00:20:32,693 --> 00:20:33,933
Why are you all dressed up?

303
00:20:34,173 --> 00:20:35,292
Go scrub.

304
00:20:36,413 --> 00:20:37,372
Scrub?

305
00:20:37,933 --> 00:20:39,653
Mom got a job as a bath scrubber.

306
00:20:40,733 --> 00:20:41,852
What for?

307
00:20:42,332 --> 00:20:44,693
What's wrong?
Think I'm embarrassing you?

308
00:20:46,253 --> 00:20:49,092
It's not that bad.
You're not allowed to go.

309
00:20:51,253 --> 00:20:53,528
Before going to college,
you're looking down on laborers?

310
00:20:53,653 --> 00:20:54,812
Don't exaggerate it.

311
00:20:55,733 --> 00:20:58,292
You're getting old.
Can't you find a lighter job?

312
00:20:58,453 --> 00:21:00,453
I'm 39. I'm still young.

313
00:21:01,173 --> 00:21:03,612
What can I do?
I'm not a college graduate.

314
00:21:04,413 --> 00:21:06,213
Being a bath scrubber
just requires strength.

315
00:21:06,328 --> 00:21:07,532
That's good.

316
00:21:07,893 --> 00:21:09,453
Alright, you two have your fun.

317
00:21:09,653 --> 00:21:10,213
Go to bed now.

318
00:21:10,693 --> 00:21:12,812
I won't see you off
at the train station tomorrow.

319
00:21:25,413 --> 00:21:26,253
What's wrong?

320
00:21:30,052 --> 00:21:31,612
Aren't you going to say goodbye to me?

321
00:21:34,092 --> 00:21:35,132
What for?

322
00:21:36,653 --> 00:21:37,976
I'll be back for winter break.

323
00:21:42,292 --> 00:21:45,173
While scrubbing people,

324
00:21:47,173 --> 00:21:48,292
pace yourself.

325
00:21:50,132 --> 00:21:51,013
Don't work too hard.

326
00:21:53,973 --> 00:21:55,608
It's your first time
going far from home.

327
00:21:57,572 --> 00:21:59,693
Take care of yourself
when I'm not around.

328
00:22:10,772 --> 00:22:12,372
Tell me if you need money.

329
00:24:13,144 --> 00:24:15,092
(Qingzhou University)

330
00:24:15,092 --> 00:24:19,532
(September 1, 2007.
I walked into Qingzhou University.)

331
00:24:20,132 --> 00:24:21,733
(Everything felt so new.)

332
00:24:22,453 --> 00:24:26,052
(But Bai Shu didn't meet me
at the station as planned.)

333
00:24:26,733 --> 00:24:29,453
(I was really worried
something had happened to her.)

334
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:35,256
(Qidaohezi Railway Station)

335
00:24:39,213 --> 00:24:40,132
He Yuqiong?

336
00:24:45,532 --> 00:24:47,612
Why are you here? What are you doing?

337
00:24:47,772 --> 00:24:49,372
The train's leaving.
Why are you so late?

338
00:24:49,372 --> 00:24:50,572
Where's Bai Shu? Is she here?

339
00:24:50,852 --> 00:24:52,812
I don't know. I'm not here for her.

340
00:24:53,013 --> 00:24:54,572
What now? We agreed to go together.

341
00:24:54,852 --> 00:24:56,532
The train's about to leave. What to do?

342
00:24:56,933 --> 00:24:58,693
You go ahead, and I'll find her.

343
00:24:59,173 --> 00:24:59,973
Alright.

344
00:25:00,292 --> 00:25:01,132
Give this to her.

345
00:25:01,213 --> 00:25:03,413
Give it to her yourself.
Don't give it to her mom, okay?

346
00:25:03,992 --> 00:25:04,532
Thanks.

347
00:25:04,532 --> 00:25:05,812
- I'm leaving. Bye.
- Take this.

348
00:25:05,933 --> 00:25:06,812
Take this. Take it.

349
00:25:06,812 --> 00:25:07,453
What is it?

350
00:25:10,372 --> 00:25:11,013
What is it?

351
00:25:12,493 --> 00:25:13,372
A hard sleeper ticket?

352
00:25:13,612 --> 00:25:15,132
I knew you'd be too stingy

353
00:25:15,132 --> 00:25:16,933
- to buy one.
- Refund it!

354
00:25:17,413 --> 00:25:18,173
Refund it!

355
00:25:18,653 --> 00:25:20,532
Just want to show off how rich you are?

356
00:25:21,653 --> 00:25:23,213
Don't give it to her mom, got it?

357
00:25:23,332 --> 00:25:24,132
Got it.

358
00:25:28,973 --> 00:25:32,132
(In that instant, I knew
He Yuqiong and I had made up.)

359
00:25:43,893 --> 00:25:44,612
Bai Shu!

360
00:25:50,532 --> 00:25:51,132
Bai Shu!

361
00:25:53,253 --> 00:25:54,013
Bai Shu!

362
00:25:56,933 --> 00:25:59,332
What's wrong? Weren't you supposed
to leave with Xiaoming?

363
00:25:59,532 --> 00:26:01,653
She'd waited for you
and almost missed the train.

364
00:26:02,292 --> 00:26:03,213
I'm sick.

365
00:26:03,532 --> 00:26:04,856
Why didn't you answer your phone?

366
00:26:05,173 --> 00:26:06,253
What's wrong?

367
00:26:08,092 --> 00:26:09,464
She wanted me to give you this.

368
00:26:14,213 --> 00:26:15,052
Thanks.

369
00:26:16,292 --> 00:26:18,852
Is something wrong? If yes, tell me.

370
00:26:23,292 --> 00:26:24,453
Bye, Bai Shu.

371
00:26:32,092 --> 00:26:32,653
Give it to me.

372
00:26:35,052 --> 00:26:35,772
Give it to me.

373
00:26:38,173 --> 00:26:38,852
Give it to me.

374
00:26:41,852 --> 00:26:43,052
The admission letter?

375
00:26:46,173 --> 00:26:47,693
And the ticket to Qingzhou?

376
00:26:52,504 --> 00:26:54,520
(Admission Letter)

377
00:26:59,893 --> 00:27:01,612
How coincidental it is.

378
00:27:02,424 --> 00:27:06,173
Had I not run into your homeroom teacher,
I wouldn't have known you got in.

379
00:27:08,453 --> 00:27:11,092
This must be what people call fate.

380
00:27:16,693 --> 00:27:17,852
That's my daughter,

381
00:27:18,893 --> 00:27:19,973
so promising.

382
00:27:26,693 --> 00:27:27,453
Hard seat.

383
00:27:29,532 --> 00:27:30,532
How shabby.

384
00:27:33,933 --> 00:27:35,612
Why didn't you tell me?

385
00:27:36,173 --> 00:27:37,772
I could've bought you a plane ticket,

386
00:27:38,733 --> 00:27:41,812
so you could fly first class comfortably
to Qingzhou.

387
00:27:49,292 --> 00:27:53,173
I've said
that lies are the most unforgivable.

388
00:27:55,292 --> 00:27:57,413
Liars must pay the price.

389
00:28:01,332 --> 00:28:03,852
You will pay for the mistake you made.

390
00:28:57,253 --> 00:29:00,772
(Xiaoming, actually,
I had a feeling from the start)

391
00:29:01,493 --> 00:29:02,852
(that I couldn't leave.)

392
00:29:05,812 --> 00:29:07,253
(Fate is really strange.)

393
00:29:08,372 --> 00:29:12,332
(I wanted to stay with my birth parents,
but they abandoned me.)

394
00:29:13,612 --> 00:29:16,852
(I wanted to get away from Ge Wenjun,
but I never could.)

395
00:29:20,013 --> 00:29:22,933
(Things don't always go
as planned in life.)

396
00:29:23,572 --> 00:29:25,453
(Or is it just my fate?)

397
00:29:36,693 --> 00:29:41,693
(Ms. Zhou said people should always
hold onto hope and courage.)

398
00:29:42,332 --> 00:29:43,653
(But where did she go?)

399
00:29:45,132 --> 00:29:46,852
(Why haven't we heard from her?)

400
00:30:03,132 --> 00:30:06,772
(Xiaoming, you must be
at Qingzhou University by now, right?)

401
00:30:08,493 --> 00:30:10,052
(I might die here.)

402
00:30:13,092 --> 00:30:14,572
Congenital heart defect.

403
00:30:14,893 --> 00:30:17,332
Even after surgery,
she needs to be careful.

404
00:30:18,052 --> 00:30:20,760
Don't overexert herself
or get too emotionally worked up.

405
00:30:21,213 --> 00:30:23,292
Right, I'm already this age.

406
00:30:23,973 --> 00:30:27,052
If anything happens to my child,
I couldn't go on living.

407
00:30:27,852 --> 00:30:29,052
Parents always worry much.

408
00:30:29,612 --> 00:30:30,292
Go check on her.

409
00:30:37,092 --> 00:30:39,772
Rest well. Don't let
your parents worry about you.

410
00:30:40,253 --> 00:30:42,013
Also, you need to focus on recovering.

411
00:30:42,253 --> 00:30:43,372
Don't make them worry, okay?

412
00:30:44,413 --> 00:30:45,493
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

413
00:30:45,493 --> 00:30:46,013
It's okay.

414
00:30:47,572 --> 00:30:49,733
You haven't eaten properly for days.

415
00:30:50,693 --> 00:30:51,733
The doctor said

416
00:30:54,973 --> 00:30:56,733
you shouldn't
eat greasy food right away.

417
00:30:57,372 --> 00:30:59,653
I made you some porridge
to help soothe your stomach.

418
00:31:05,272 --> 00:31:05,933
Here.

419
00:31:09,572 --> 00:31:10,973
What? What's wrong?

420
00:31:12,653 --> 00:31:13,933
That's hot.

421
00:31:13,933 --> 00:31:14,584
This...

422
00:31:14,584 --> 00:31:15,173
No.

423
00:31:15,453 --> 00:31:16,728
We need to get this treated.

424
00:31:16,856 --> 00:31:17,464
Come on!

425
00:31:17,693 --> 00:31:18,456
It's fine.

426
00:31:18,653 --> 00:31:19,812
- You're injured.
- It's okay.

427
00:31:20,312 --> 00:31:20,893
Come on.

428
00:31:21,052 --> 00:31:21,852
- Just wipe it off.
- Let's go.

429
00:31:21,933 --> 00:31:23,092
Go get it treated. Come on.

430
00:31:23,332 --> 00:31:23,852
Be careful.

431
00:31:23,852 --> 00:31:24,440
Okay.

432
00:31:35,653 --> 00:31:38,332
(My three roommates are all amazing.)

433
00:31:39,213 --> 00:31:41,092
(Sun Xiaomi is a violin enthusiast.)

434
00:31:41,944 --> 00:31:44,413
(She practices the violin
for two hours every day.)

435
00:31:45,812 --> 00:31:48,852
(Cheche is excellent at studying.)

436
00:31:49,733 --> 00:31:51,653
(I can barely handle one degree.)

437
00:31:52,013 --> 00:31:53,612
(Yet she's pursuing a double major.)

438
00:31:54,812 --> 00:31:57,453
(Plus, she's into wire art.)

439
00:31:58,253 --> 00:32:02,052
(Ordinary wire
becomes art in her hands.)

440
00:32:02,973 --> 00:32:06,893
(And Jingwei always spends hours
on the phone with her boyfriend.)

441
00:32:06,973 --> 00:32:08,292
I love you too.

442
00:32:10,812 --> 00:32:12,812
I have fencing now.
I have to hang up. Bye!

443
00:32:17,013 --> 00:32:19,852
(She's also a fencing enthusiast.)

444
00:32:20,693 --> 00:32:22,013
(She's won some competitions.)

445
00:32:22,292 --> 00:32:26,292
Who wants to go fencing with me?

446
00:32:26,653 --> 00:32:28,213
I checked. It's closed.

447
00:32:30,453 --> 00:32:31,132
Boring.

448
00:32:33,653 --> 00:32:36,653
(I struggled so much
just to get into this new group.)

449
00:32:37,092 --> 00:32:39,332
(But I realized in this group,)

450
00:32:39,532 --> 00:32:41,173
(I'm the dumbest bird)

451
00:32:41,592 --> 00:32:44,056
(and a clueless one.)

452
00:32:50,772 --> 00:32:51,453
Bai Shu?

453
00:32:54,733 --> 00:32:55,653
Are you Bai Shu?

454
00:32:56,612 --> 00:32:57,372
Who are you?

455
00:32:58,332 --> 00:32:59,653
Uncle Haozi.

456
00:33:00,332 --> 00:33:02,532
Wang Hao, your mom's buddy.

457
00:33:03,812 --> 00:33:04,493
She's not here.

458
00:33:08,052 --> 00:33:09,493
I'm here to see you.

459
00:33:09,973 --> 00:33:11,973
You're all grown up now.

460
00:33:12,933 --> 00:33:14,572
When I picked you up from Wuchuan,

461
00:33:15,052 --> 00:33:16,253
you were only this big.

462
00:33:17,453 --> 00:33:18,173
Wuchuan?

463
00:33:20,332 --> 00:33:21,493
You brought me here?

464
00:33:23,173 --> 00:33:25,532
That was eighteen years ago.

465
00:33:26,493 --> 00:33:30,332
One day your mom said,
"Wang Hao, help me with a private job."

466
00:33:30,812 --> 00:33:33,933
So I drove her to Wuchuan.

467
00:33:34,693 --> 00:33:35,812
On the way back,

468
00:33:36,332 --> 00:33:37,893
there was an extra passenger, you.

469
00:33:38,612 --> 00:33:40,332
Did you ever meet my birth parents?

470
00:33:41,493 --> 00:33:42,092
No.

471
00:33:42,372 --> 00:33:43,933
Your mom went to get you herself.

472
00:33:44,173 --> 00:33:45,332
I waited at the hostel.

473
00:33:46,173 --> 00:33:47,453
Did she tell you

474
00:33:48,213 --> 00:33:49,893
why my birth parents abandoned me?

475
00:33:52,372 --> 00:33:55,132
Why dwell on it?
Just focus on living well now.

476
00:33:56,213 --> 00:33:58,572
People shouldn't obsess

477
00:33:58,733 --> 00:34:00,572
over the past, right?

478
00:34:04,132 --> 00:34:04,653
Okay.

479
00:34:05,453 --> 00:34:07,852
If you really want to find them,
I'll ask around for you.

480
00:34:09,373 --> 00:34:10,132
Really?

481
00:34:17,304 --> 00:34:19,096
Where's my child?

482
00:34:19,096 --> 00:34:19,933
I'm sorry!

483
00:34:19,933 --> 00:34:21,853
This is how you care for your patients?

484
00:34:22,172 --> 00:34:23,064
Head, what's wrong?

485
00:34:23,252 --> 00:34:24,692
Who's in charge of bed three?

486
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:26,092
What's wrong with you?

487
00:34:26,092 --> 00:34:28,052
I'm sorry!
We've sent people to look for her.

488
00:34:28,052 --> 00:34:28,853
I'll call the cops.

489
00:34:28,853 --> 00:34:30,132
Please, don't!

490
00:34:30,132 --> 00:34:31,212
I'll call the police!

491
00:34:31,212 --> 00:34:32,013
I'm sorry!

492
00:34:32,013 --> 00:34:32,973
No need to be so tense.

493
00:34:39,692 --> 00:34:40,413
Sorry.

494
00:34:40,773 --> 00:34:41,612
I'm really sorry.

495
00:34:41,612 --> 00:34:42,373
Sorry.

496
00:34:42,584 --> 00:34:43,813
Ms. Zhang, I'm so sorry.

497
00:34:44,933 --> 00:34:45,813
It's okay.

498
00:34:48,013 --> 00:34:48,572
It's all good.

499
00:34:50,572 --> 00:34:52,333
I agree attending the normal college.

500
00:34:52,973 --> 00:34:54,052
It's not against the rules.

501
00:34:54,732 --> 00:34:55,813
But I have one condition.

502
00:34:59,893 --> 00:35:00,572
Go ahead.

503
00:35:01,893 --> 00:35:02,893
I want to live on campus.

504
00:35:08,692 --> 00:35:10,612
Let's go see a movie. A new one's out.

505
00:35:10,612 --> 00:35:11,413
See a movie?

506
00:35:11,853 --> 00:35:12,493
That's great.

507
00:35:12,692 --> 00:35:13,692
I have to go, bye.

508
00:35:13,692 --> 00:35:15,013
Come on, Xiaoming. Come on.

509
00:35:15,252 --> 00:35:16,532
- Come on, let's go.
- Let's go, we're getting late.

510
00:35:16,532 --> 00:35:17,333
Come on!

511
00:35:17,333 --> 00:35:18,052
I'm not going.

512
00:35:18,052 --> 00:35:18,813
- You guys go.
- Let's go.

513
00:35:18,973 --> 00:35:20,132
- I have to study.
- Hurry up.

514
00:35:20,132 --> 00:35:20,973
- The exam is coming.
- Let's go.

515
00:35:31,453 --> 00:35:32,293
You guys go.

516
00:35:32,696 --> 00:35:35,333
Tell me how it was
when you come back, okay?

517
00:35:36,052 --> 00:35:37,652
Okay, we'll act it out for you.

518
00:35:39,132 --> 00:35:40,692
Just go, stop dawdling.

519
00:35:40,692 --> 00:35:41,893
- Go.
- Let's go.

520
00:35:52,692 --> 00:35:55,493
(School started,
but Bai Shu still hasn't arrived.)

521
00:35:56,652 --> 00:35:59,453
(I called her home several times,
but no one answered.)

522
00:36:00,453 --> 00:36:01,933
(Could something happen to her?)

523
00:36:19,813 --> 00:36:20,333
Shu.

524
00:36:21,333 --> 00:36:22,132
Uncle Wang Hao.

525
00:36:23,132 --> 00:36:23,732
Get in.

526
00:36:24,172 --> 00:36:25,933
I'll take you
to eat something delicious.

527
00:36:27,052 --> 00:36:27,853
I'm not eating.

528
00:36:45,413 --> 00:36:46,132
What's it?

529
00:36:46,453 --> 00:36:47,172
A phone.

530
00:36:49,413 --> 00:36:50,172
I don't need it.

531
00:36:52,132 --> 00:36:54,252
You're a college student,
and you need a phone.

532
00:36:55,532 --> 00:36:57,493
Do you know what kind of people
don't need phones?

533
00:36:57,853 --> 00:36:59,092
The one no one contacts.

534
00:37:13,652 --> 00:37:15,032
The first step in using a phone

535
00:37:15,032 --> 00:37:17,652
is to save the people you need
into your contacts.

536
00:37:21,973 --> 00:37:23,132
I don't have anyone I need.

537
00:37:23,896 --> 00:37:26,252
It's not about people you need,
but people who need you.

538
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,933
Maybe he'll bring you wealth.

539
00:37:33,732 --> 00:37:36,092
Hello, is this Shu?

540
00:37:36,652 --> 00:37:38,252
Yes, it's me, Uncle Wang Hao.

541
00:37:39,256 --> 00:37:41,912
Recently, I got a shipment from overseas

542
00:37:41,912 --> 00:37:43,652
with hundreds of types
of small appliances.

543
00:37:44,013 --> 00:37:47,192
I need their English manuals
translated into Chinese.

544
00:37:48,052 --> 00:37:50,092
Hiring a translation company
is just too expensive.

545
00:37:50,493 --> 00:37:53,933
Right, I suddenly remembered
you're studying English.

546
00:37:54,853 --> 00:37:55,692
You can do it.

547
00:37:57,732 --> 00:37:58,293
How is it?

548
00:37:59,933 --> 00:38:01,212
You're asking for my help?

549
00:38:01,944 --> 00:38:02,933
You can send them to me.

550
00:38:03,352 --> 00:38:05,532
If I can handle it,
I'll help you translate.

551
00:38:06,052 --> 00:38:08,252
Okay, I'll pay you per piece.

552
00:38:09,092 --> 00:38:11,092
100 yuan per piece,
regardless of word count.

553
00:38:11,413 --> 00:38:13,773
Even if it's only three words,
you come out ahead.

554
00:38:14,252 --> 00:38:16,172
But if it's translating a booklet,

555
00:38:16,853 --> 00:38:18,333
then you'll bear with it, okay?

556
00:38:21,092 --> 00:38:22,333
How much does

557
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,216
a translation company charge?

558
00:38:26,013 --> 00:38:28,732
Overall, it should be about
three times what you're charging.

559
00:38:30,692 --> 00:38:33,092
Then I'll charge you 200 yuan,
regardless of word count.

560
00:38:33,973 --> 00:38:34,572
Why?

561
00:38:36,252 --> 00:38:38,933
You charge 100,
a translation company charges you 300.

562
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:42,212
The price I can command
is between 100 and 300.

563
00:38:42,612 --> 00:38:45,252
But I'm not a professional,
I can't charge you 300.

564
00:38:46,212 --> 00:38:47,532
But I can't accept 100 either.

565
00:38:47,933 --> 00:38:49,048
Because my pricing

566
00:38:49,592 --> 00:38:52,728
sets the rate for future college students
doing part-time work for you.

567
00:38:53,688 --> 00:38:55,813
So I'll take the middle value, 200 yuan.

568
00:38:56,568 --> 00:38:57,172
Deal.

569
00:38:59,572 --> 00:39:00,132
Thank you.

570
00:39:07,853 --> 00:39:09,933
(I've always wanted to leave Qidaohezi.)

571
00:39:10,252 --> 00:39:13,453
(But now that I'm gone,
I really miss it.)

572
00:39:14,652 --> 00:39:15,933
(Are they all doing okay?)

573
00:39:26,212 --> 00:39:27,532
Hello, college girl.

574
00:39:28,413 --> 00:39:29,853
Finally called me?

575
00:39:36,952 --> 00:39:37,773
Why no sound?

576
00:39:39,384 --> 00:39:39,973
Hello?

577
00:39:41,092 --> 00:39:41,933
Ran out of money?

578
00:39:42,973 --> 00:39:44,252
It's only been early this month.

579
00:39:44,933 --> 00:39:46,612
Did I ask you for money?

580
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:48,373
Unbelievable.

581
00:39:49,493 --> 00:39:50,692
Then why did you call me?

582
00:39:50,808 --> 00:39:51,832
Dialed the wrong number.

583
00:39:53,813 --> 00:39:55,973
Hello, daughter,
how's the cafeteria food?

584
00:39:56,413 --> 00:39:56,973
Not bad.

585
00:39:58,172 --> 00:39:59,640
Getting along with your classmates?

586
00:39:59,732 --> 00:40:01,453
So-so, pretty good.

587
00:40:01,973 --> 00:40:02,732
How about studying?

588
00:40:04,172 --> 00:40:06,172
What's wrong with you?
Why keep repeating this?

589
00:40:06,333 --> 00:40:08,773
Are you a broken record?
Every second costs money.

590
00:40:11,612 --> 00:40:12,692
I haven't finished.

591
00:40:22,692 --> 00:40:23,612
Why hung up on me?

592
00:40:24,092 --> 00:40:25,013
You're getting bold.

593
00:40:25,493 --> 00:40:26,853
You eat well and study hard.

594
00:40:27,256 --> 00:40:28,813
Get along well with your classmates.

595
00:40:30,453 --> 00:40:31,333
Any bath scrubber?

596
00:40:33,092 --> 00:40:33,612
I have to go.

597
00:40:33,612 --> 00:40:34,933
Yes, coming.

598
00:40:51,992 --> 00:40:52,532
Hello?

599
00:40:56,652 --> 00:40:57,333
Who is this?

600
00:40:57,813 --> 00:40:59,493
Guess who I am.

601
00:41:00,212 --> 00:41:00,933
Insane.

602
00:41:01,293 --> 00:41:02,712
It's me, He Yuqiong.

603
00:41:02,712 --> 00:41:03,572
Did I scare you?

604
00:41:03,773 --> 00:41:04,453
He Yuqiong?

605
00:41:05,652 --> 00:41:07,853
I'm testing phone numbers,
don't save this number.

606
00:41:07,853 --> 00:41:09,293
Save it after I get my new number.

607
00:41:09,853 --> 00:41:11,212
How did you get my number?

608
00:41:11,732 --> 00:41:14,532
Xiaofei ate one of my popsicles
and gave it to me.

609
00:41:16,652 --> 00:41:18,132
Sound like you didn't want it.

610
00:41:18,132 --> 00:41:18,973
Then don't call me.

611
00:41:19,212 --> 00:41:20,212
Why are you calling me?

612
00:41:21,013 --> 00:41:22,532
That's enough, or I'll charge you.

613
00:41:23,013 --> 00:41:24,092
I'll pay you extra, bro.

614
00:41:24,293 --> 00:41:25,212
Alright, go ahead.

615
00:41:27,532 --> 00:41:30,052
Tell me about your recent bad luck
to cheer me up.

616
00:41:33,052 --> 00:41:35,373
I've been really unlucky.

617
00:41:36,013 --> 00:41:37,252
The campus is huge.

618
00:41:37,252 --> 00:41:40,013
I'm exhausted from running
to different classrooms.

619
00:41:40,652 --> 00:41:44,532
And last time at the cafeteria,
the line was incredibly long.

620
00:41:44,532 --> 00:41:46,813
After finally reaching the front,
I forgot my meal card.

621
00:41:49,453 --> 00:41:50,132
And then?

622
00:41:50,680 --> 00:41:52,172
Then I went back to get my card.

623
00:41:52,453 --> 00:41:53,813
After I finally bought my meal,

624
00:41:54,052 --> 00:41:55,132
I was about to eat,

625
00:41:55,373 --> 00:41:56,853
but ended up biting into a paperclip.

626
00:41:56,973 --> 00:41:58,013
Tell me I'm not unlucky.

627
00:42:00,692 --> 00:42:01,773
Why are you laughing?

628
00:42:02,692 --> 00:42:03,413
Stop it!

629
00:42:08,333 --> 00:42:11,333
(He Yuqiong's call was like a lifeline.)

630
00:42:11,813 --> 00:42:13,092
(Without that lifeline,)

631
00:42:13,496 --> 00:42:18,172
(I, alone in Qingzhou,
would have drowned in loneliness.)

632
00:42:22,264 --> 00:42:24,132
(La City Normal College)

633
00:42:24,132 --> 00:42:25,172
The ball's gone.

634
00:42:25,413 --> 00:42:26,413
Insane.

635
00:42:26,853 --> 00:42:27,453
What?

636
00:42:36,132 --> 00:42:36,652
Zhang Fang.

637
00:42:37,624 --> 00:42:38,252
Thanks.

638
00:42:41,652 --> 00:42:43,092
Why do you know I am here?

639
00:42:44,973 --> 00:42:46,413
I drive trucks all over the place.

640
00:42:46,732 --> 00:42:47,853
Just ask around.

641
00:42:48,172 --> 00:42:50,853
Besides, gathering info
is part of the job for us.

642
00:42:51,973 --> 00:42:52,853
Where did you park?

643
00:42:53,112 --> 00:42:54,282
The school didn't let me in,

644
00:42:54,282 --> 00:42:56,052
so I parked
at the building material market.

645
00:42:56,252 --> 00:42:57,893
I have to haul timber to Xi'an tonight.

646
00:42:58,936 --> 00:42:59,493
Right.

647
00:43:00,572 --> 00:43:01,893
Why don't we call Xiaoming?

648
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
